    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise shift action, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced subframe and a well-sorted suspension geometry that minimizes body roll. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the core mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and bushings\u2014have been meticulously maintained to preserve the car's legendary handling and 8,000 RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
