    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle presents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor road-wear typical of its age, such as small stone chips on the front fascia and a faint scuff on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolsters, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced regularly, with recent maintenance including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth, quiet ride that reflects its careful ownership history. This is a solid, dependable car that balances performance with everyday practicality.",
